<p><p>RichTextArea component: a rich text user input field which allows the user to select text styles, and insert/manipulate objects such as links, images, enumerated lists, or tables. This component may not contain children.</p><p>Security warning: HTML input provided by this component should be considered potentially malicious. Directly rendering the HTML entered by one user to other users of a multi-user application without first "cleaning" it could be disastrous to the other users. For example, a user could potentially embed JavaScript code in URLs that would execute in the other users' browsers. Any cleaning operations must be performed on the client that will render such HTML (not the client sending it) or on a central trusted server.</p></p>











